---
title: Where are Pokémon Studio's logs?
seoDescription: You can find Pokémon Studio's log in %appdata%/Pokémon Studio/logs
publishDate: '2022-09-30 17:20:00'
order: 0
---

The Pokémon Studio's logs are located into `%appdata%/Pokémon Studio/logs`. Those logs are pretty usefull when the app crashes (black screen). So if we ask for them, send us `renderer.log` and `main.log` files!

![renderer.log, Studio's log](./images/image_2022-09-30_172249777.png)

